# LeakSanitizer suppressions for known Qt offscreen/minimal platform plugin leaks in CI
# These allocations are created by Qt platform initialization and may remain at process exit
# on headless runners. We suppress only framework-level noise, not project code paths.
leak:QScreen::QScreen
leak:QPlatformScreen::QPlatformScreen
leak:QWindowSystemInterface::handleScreenAdded
leak:QtSharedPointer::ExternalRefCountData::getAndRef(QObject const*)
leak:libqoffscreen.so
leak:QObject::QObject(QObject*)
